source.name: FY 2009-10 And FY 2010-11 Budget
source.description: This shows the adopted budgets for all San Francisco Departments for two fiscal years - FY 2009-10 and FY 2010-2011. It is organized by Organization(Department and Division), Service (Program), Fund, and Type of Revenue or Expenditure (with details: Character, Object and Sub-object).
